<h3>PPUSingle( [ hi ], [ lo ], [ value ])</h3>
PPUSingle writes a single byte to the memory address specified by the two first bytes.
<code>

    // Write a single byte "0" to memory address $23C0 (color attribute)
    PPUSingle($23,$C0, 0);

    // Same is...

    // Point to first colour attribute in first nametable $23C0
    PPUPoint($23,$C0);
    // Write walue zero = four tiles use tile palette 0
    PPUWrite(0);


</code>
